highlights.text: “Falle og slå seg” by Ari Bajgora has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 69 days straight.
Vestavind has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Ligga” is the highest at #1.
“Takedown” by HUNTR/X, EJAE, AUDREY NUNA, REI AMI, and KPop Demon Hunters Cast is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 12 spots at #67.
“Keiser i nye klær” by Enebarn is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #19.
